        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''I'm not one of them ban-the-mines people. If someone's coming to attack your house, you've got a right to defend yourself any way you can. But do it right. If you've put mines in, it's your job then to take them out.''</p>
        <p>ROSS CHAMBERLAIN, an Australian helping to remove land mines in Afghanistan. [A4]</p>
      </block>
